{"tid":154191,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"十首流行文化中的古典音樂","createTime":"2017-03-13T06:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T14:23:16.000Z","uid":66320,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"130d3c663939f8825b71ab6aef1a6f460eac12fa","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"想必很多人首次接觸古典音樂都並非在華麗的音樂廳，反而是在電視或電影銀幕上。<br />\n<br />\n這篇文章就為大家搜羅十首流行文化中常見的古典音樂，讓大家好好回味。<br />\n<br />\n1. 理查 &middot; 史特勞斯：查拉圖斯特拉如是說（R.Strauss: <em>Also Sprach Zarathustra</em>）<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vWF1glZWQa8&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvWF1glZWQa8%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=bd4dcf37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vWF1glZWQa8&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n1968年科幻電影《2001太空漫遊》（<em>2001 A Space Odyssey</em>）引用了本曲的第一部份《破曉》作為開首，讓觀眾留下了深刻的印象。有趣的是，樂曲和電影兩者皆是受到德國哲學家尼采的同名著作《查拉圖斯特拉如是說》的啟發而創作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 華格納：女武神的飛行（Wagner: <em>Ride of the Valkyries</em>）<br />\n<br />\n<em><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wi0nzmqp47A&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWi0nzmqp47A%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=0117582e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wi0nzmqp47A&amp;feature=youtu.be</a></em><br />\n<br />\n想必這應該是本文章中最廣為人知的曲子了。1979年的越戰電影《現代啟示錄》（<em>Apocalypse Now</em>）中的UH-1直升機飛行片段，配樂就是這首了。氣勢磅礴的音樂襯托出殘酷無情的戰爭，令這片段成為影史上的經典。<br />\n<br />\n當然，女武神們的旅程並未完結，往後數十年的電影都有她們的蹤影（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/muzikcom/videos/10154181342541857/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmuzikcom%2Fvideos%2F10154181342541857%2F&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=72ab1c64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/muzikcom/videos/10154181342541857/</a>）出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 羅西尼：威廉泰爾序曲（Rossini: <em>William Tell Overture</em>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GqHNZPkl0qE&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGqHNZPkl0qE%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=870bfe69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GqHNZPkl0qE&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n威廉泰爾是位瑞士傳說中的英雄，1829年意大利作曲家羅西尼根據德國劇作家席勒的劇作《威廉&middot;泰爾》創作了同名歌劇，而其序曲則成名了古典音樂界中的名曲。香港亞視<del>（已倒閉）</del>曾以此曲作為賽馬節日的主題曲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 柴可夫斯基：胡桃夾子組曲（Tchaikovsky: <em>The Nutcracker Suite</em>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8At8zfh_o3E&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8At8zfh_o3E%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d10d2391\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8At8zfh_o3E&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n這是一首每逢聖誕節都會聽到的曲子，其實是芭蕾舞劇《胡桃夾子組曲》中的《糖果仙子之舞》（<em>Dance of the Sugar Plum Fairy</em>）。原作劇情是基於一部叫作《胡桃鉗與老鼠王》的故事來創作。《胡桃夾子》的故事大約是這樣的： 多年前的聖誕節平安夜晚上，小女孩克拉拉得到了一份很特別的聖誕禮物：一個軍官造型的胡桃夾子。入夜後，這個胡桃夾子竟然動了起來，領導著一群玩具，和老鼠兵作戰！在危急之際，克拉拉用劍刺傷了老鼠王，勝負在一瞬間扭轉。<br />\n<br />\n柴氏將之加譜了芭蕾舞音樂，成為現今所廣為大眾認識的《胡桃夾子》。除了《糖果仙子之舞》外，樂曲的其他部分亦常在流行文化中出現。<br />\n<br />\n題外話，筆者曾經見過此曲還被引用到萬聖節的影片中，雖然看此有點突兀，但其實還不錯的...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 普契尼：《賈尼斯基基》（Puccini: <em>Gianni Schicchi</em>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyQ4vkTwc4E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcyQ4vkTwc4E&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5cf099a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyQ4vkTwc4E</a><br />\n<br />\n出自意大利作曲家普契尼手筆，歌劇《賈尼斯基基》中的詠嘆調《親愛的爸爸》（<em>O mio babbino caro</em>）可謂無人不曉。這首詠嘆調基本上是每位女高音的必唱曲目，但同時亦出現在眾多流行文化中。例如以上的1985年英國電影《窗外有藍天》（<em>A Room with a View</em>）、《戇豆放大假》（<em>Mr Bean&rsquo;s Holiday</em>）、The East Village Opera Company的改編（<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GkbKWZ8a4a8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGkbKWZ8a4a8&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=1c118777\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GkbKWZ8a4a8</a>）等。"},{"pid":"f2bc50d203eca1609de690402dfc481595f741fc","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"6. 拉赫曼尼諾夫：帕格尼尼主題狂想曲（Rachmaninov: <em>Rhapsody on a Theme of Paganini</em>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h4N1mxN5JbU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh4N1mxN5JbU&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=31bc79e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h4N1mxN5JbU</a><br />\n<br />\n創作於1934年，拉赫曼尼諾夫以著名小提琴家帕格尼尼所創作的著名隨想曲《第24號隨想曲》（<em>Caprice No.24</em>）加以改編而成。本曲一共有24個變奏，但當中最為著名的當然就是變奏十八。1980年的電影《時光倒流七十年》（<em>Somewhere in Time</em>）則多次引用此曲，和電影中浪漫的情節配合得天衣無縫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7. 巴哈：第三管弦樂組曲 BWV.1068（J.S. Bach: <em>Orchestral Suite No.3 in D, BWV 1068</em>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gbUYwvM7PlQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgbUYwvM7PlQ&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6249ff72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gbUYwvM7PlQ</a><br />\n<br />\n原曲創作於1717-1723年，其中第二樂章被人稱為&rdquo;<em>Air on G</em>&rdquo;。於18世紀曾被改編成小提琴和鋼琴（或管風琴、其他弦樂）。現今兩個版本都有同樣的知名度，在流行文化中亦處處可見此曲的蹤影。除了出現在日本動畫電影《新世紀福音戰士劇場版》（<em>The End of Evangelion</em>）外，1995年的犯罪電影《七宗罪》（<em>Seven</em>）（<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r6bzgNHeYAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr6bzgNHeYAQ&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5fab9955\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r6bzgNHeYAQ</a>）也引用了此曲。旋律和畫面上的衝突以及不和諧，更為影片增添一份味道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8. 歌舒詠：藍色狂想曲（Gershwin: <em>Rhapsody in Blue</em>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IzuIKXPLEcE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIzuIKXPLEcE&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6011e4e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IzuIKXPLEcE</a><br />\n<br />\n曲子的原名是《美國幻想曲》，《藍色狂想曲》是由歌舒詠在參觀完某個畫展之後所提出的。這首樂曲在當時的美國就已經很受歡迎，其融合了古典和爵士樂的風格。樂曲完成的翌年就已經售出過百萬張唱片，深深地影響了往後的藝術創作人，當中包括電影導演活地亞倫等人。而十年前風靡亞洲的日本劇集《交響情人夢》更選用了此曲作為片尾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9. 薩拉薩蒂：流浪者之歌（Sarasate: <em>Zigeunerweisen</em>）<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9QBF-uqqF1M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9QBF-uqqF1M&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=53af5bb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9QBF-uqqF1M</a><br />\n <br />\n《流浪者之歌》是西班牙作曲家薩拉薩蒂於1878年完成的一首管弦樂隊伴奏的小提琴曲，為每位小提琴家的必備曲目。在流行文化中亦被廣泛應用，除了周星馳2004年電影《功夫》以外，亦出現在由日本導演鈴木清順所執導的同名電影《流浪者之歌》中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10. 巴哈：d小調托卡塔與賦格 BWV.565（J.S. Bach: <em>Toccata and Fugue in d minor, BWV 565</em>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z4MQ7GzE6HY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz4MQ7GzE6HY&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d476a485\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z4MQ7GzE6HY</a><br />\n<br />\n本曲是巴哈最為有名的風琴作品，曾被多次改編成不同版本，而在流行文化中亦被引用過無數次。以上就是1940年迪士尼電影《幻想曲》（<em>Fantasia</em>）中的片段，電影主要分為七個部分，由八首古典音樂組成：主要由七部古典音樂組成：《d小調托卡塔與賦格》、《胡桃夾子組曲》、杜卡的《魔法師的弟子》（<em>L&rsquo;apprenti sorcier</em>）、史特拉汶斯基的《春之祭》（<em>Le Sacre du Printemps</em>）、貝多芬的《第六交響曲》、龐契埃利的《時辰之舞》（<em>Dance of the Hours</em>）、穆索斯基的《荒山之夜》（<em>Night on Bald Mountain</em>）和舒伯特的《聖母頌》（<em>Ave Mari</em>a）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://diemusikzeitung.com/2017/03/13/%E5%8D%81%E9%A6%96%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiemusikzeitung.com%2F2017%2F03%2F13%2F%25E5%258D%2581%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%2585%25B8%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%2F&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=887f9c94\" target=\"_blank\">https://diemusikzeitung.com/2017/03/13/%E5%8D%81%E9%A6%96%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82/</a><br />\n<br />\n鍾意嘅請大家like：[url]<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/diemusikzeitung[/ur]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdiemusikzeitung%5B%2Fur%5D&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=15dcaa53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/diemusikzeitung[/ur]</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反應好再寫多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa6281c3276c31d1449f84db5611cce5a893682","tid":154191,"uid":90837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:31:12.000Z","msg":"Bach Italian concerto<br />\n陪伴香港25年"},{"pid":"125bdd750310d19ec705560e1808f28b56d22e13","tid":154191,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a894531474210cb23439139d209299763f53fc","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Bach Italian concerto<br />\n陪伴香港25年</blockquote><br />\n有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc773147479574d3a51d51c634edd67c621bcc2b","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e187e6fd2bf1b7c7713eb6f460db1e31eb4dc1e8","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T11:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd13d87b857ce6bb30b3e0886135fd8dbd14451","tid":154191,"uid":42601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"LM支持"},{"pid":"e7a5803191b33a1136e4042949002b0899899111","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LM支持</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5007a236b9f2df780a4d75adf093d72917fdd232","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8c022c2cc92aafa00b0008c419744d5deeb190","tid":154191,"uid":34077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"lm學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bcc0f480ca66469885f519506303088134a20d","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e59bea2c25b2cfb9a42db59d4bd5074e293bc5","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0badadeadce39e62d6405d51c715548d4d95aabb","tid":154191,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:12:00.000Z","msg":"高汁"},{"pid":"45e6f780cf9adf5581dcf12a0a74f95221f748f3","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aae640290e5fda2caf473c1090d4f4cb7fa57a5","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d945afb0e7ff2a1941a247ab1704411eb79a2d35","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0914b5f53f935c79c5382d8ce639249434fefd6a","tid":154191,"uid":66320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}